遠洛克威-莫特大道車站是洛克威線的東端總站，建於混凝土高架橋上，設有一個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和兩條軌道。軌道在月台東北端不遠的[[止衝擋|止衝擋]]結束<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.subwaynut.com/ind/far_rockaway_motta/index.php|title=Far Rockaway-Mott Avenue (A) - The SubwayNut|last=Cox|first=Jeremiah|website=www.subwaynut.com|access-date=January 2, 2017|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706140035/http://www.subwaynut.com/ind/far_rockaway_motta/index.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。過去連接現時[[長島鐵路|長島鐵路]]的{{link-en|遠洛克威車站 (長島鐵路)|Far Rockaway (LIRR station)|遠洛克威車站}}的軌道已經拆除，而現時轉乘該鐵路需要步行三個街區<ref name=NYTimes-FarRkwy-ShopCtr-July1956 />。{{link-en|紐約市交通局|New York City Department of Transportation}}市立停車場設施位於車站以東海灘22街和海灘21街之間，與Q22、QM17和N33號線使用的巴士總站相鄰<ref name="NYCDOT-MunicipalParking">{{cite web|title=Municipal Parking Facilities|url=http://www.nyc.gov/html/dot/html/motorist/parkinglist.shtml|publisher=[[New_York_City_Department_of_Transportation|New York City Department of Transportation]]|access-date=2017-07-18|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503001143/http://www.nyc.gov/html/dot/html/motorist/parkinglist.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MTABusTime-Q22">{{cite web|title=MTA Bus Time: Q22 Rockaway Beach Blvd - Beach Channel Dr|url=http://bustime.mta.info/#q22|website=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|mta.info]]|publisher=[[MTA_Bus_Time|MTA Bus Time]]|access-date=2017-07-18|archive-date=2015-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107093818/http://bustime.mta.info/#q22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

